model.name: Heiland2019 - Two compartment model of NAD biosynthesis and consumption

body.p: The model is based on MODEL1905220001 but has two compartments that have different composition of the biosynthetic enzymes NADA and NamPT. One compartment contains in addition NNMT, the other one does not. Both compartments are competing for a common Nam source.
